<p>We will try to do this in tandem with the calendar configuration setup that will need to take place. However, I'm tentative about upgrading everyone right now as I'd rather more technically adept users have Lion unless its been packaged with the system already or circumstances mean they need it right now.</p>
<p>We simply don't have the scale for training or expertise in house and our audience will generally not gravitate to some of the new paradigms without assistance. Towards December is more useful to me.</p>